      "role": "user",
      "content": "that bell's theorem thing sounds complicated lol. is it basically saying there's some kind of invisible logic or hidden mechanism that we just can't see yet? like, is there something \"under the hood\" making it happen that we're missing?",
      "source": "evaluator"
